headline: Evercore ISI Group Maintains In-Line on MetLife, Lowers Price Target to $95
summary: Evercore ISI Group  analyst Thomas Gallagher   maintains MetLife (NYSE:MET) with a In-Line and lowers the price target from $97 to $95.

headline: 5 Insightful Analyst Questions From MetLife’s Q4 Earnings Call

headline: 1 Insurance Stock with Impressive Fundamentals and 2 Facing Headwinds
summary: Insurance companies serve as the backbone of risk management, providing essential protection and financial security for individuals and businesses. But concerns about claims severity and tightening regulations have tempered enthusiasm, limiting the industry’s gains to 3.4% over the past six months. This return lagged the S&P 500’s 9.1% climb.
